    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>一个关于生命中出现的爱，失去，和迷茫的游戏。</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >亲爱的玩家，我们很想将游戏翻译成中文，由于我们是一个非常小型的工作室，目前没有足够的资金。如果你们愿意支持我们，请将游戏加入愿望单——愿望单数量越多，我们就越有机会获得翻译资金——一旦我们有能力，我们一定会尽快完成翻译！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2161830/extras/2f2285708c9bec85625f55edcf32321c.poster.avif?t=1770993012\" width=490 height=276 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2161830/extras/2f2285708c9bec85625f55edcf32321c.webm?t=1770993012\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2161830/extras/2f2285708c9bec85625f55edcf32321c.mp4?t=1770993012\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >[b在试图逃离过去的旅途上，凛来到了一座陌生的城市，并且在神秘的真实之上（Truer than You）开启了新的生活与工作，这是一家专注于为真实情景出租演员的公司。[/b] </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2161830/extras/20b115d0dde5e232e36fb06577c6d6f3.avif?t=1770993012\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2161830/extras_big/20b115d0dde5e232e36fb06577c6d6f3.avif?t=1770993012 width=800 height=166 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >现在将由你带领凛，在不违反公司准则或暴露自己的情况下完成所有工作。做出不同的选择来引导各种状况，并通过对话来获得高评分。根据准则，你不可以与客户有私人关系。但是万一你喜欢上谁了呢？ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2161830/extras/ce2f7027555e5587c7fac93637f6fc5e.poster.avif?t=1770993012\" width=490 height=276 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2161830/extras/ce2f7027555e5587c7fac93637f6fc5e.webm?t=1770993012\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2161830/extras/ce2f7027555e5587c7fac93637f6fc5e.mp4?t=1770993012\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >更何况，逃离自己的思绪是可能的吗？又或者扮演成别人能使你更接近真实的自己？ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2161830/extras/7e977f34571ea42fec7437a69ab4ab05.avif?t=1770993012\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2161830/extras_big/7e977f34571ea42fec7437a69ab4ab05.avif?t=1770993012 width=800 height=166 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >💎 探索各种与真实性和社会角色有关的人际关系和困境 <br>💎 与三位角色建立更深层的联系并揭示他们的背景故事</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >💎 丰富的角色和人际关系</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >💎 从1100多个选项中作出选择并走向不同结局</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >💎 流畅的对话机制 - 自己选择说话的时机（又或者保持沉默）</p>",
